Hello, sir, take this flower from
the Religious Consciousness Church.
先生，请收下醒悟教的花朵

31
00:03:47,495 --> 00:03:49,497
Would you care...
你可否…

32
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:06,639
- Hey, Larry, where's the forklift?
- Forklift?
-莱利，铲车呢？
-铲车？

33
00:04:06,931 --> 00:04:09,601
It's over there
by the baggage loader.
在那边，行李装机旁

34
00:04:13,313 --> 00:04:15,064
Look out!
小心！

35
00:04:26,075 --> 00:04:28,161
- Elaine.
- Ted!
-绮莲
-泰德！

36
00:04:28,912 --> 00:04:30,830
I came home early
and found your note.
我早了回家，看到你的便条

37
00:04:31,122 --> 00:04:34,792
I guess you meant for me
to read it later. I've got to talk to you.
你大概是想我稍后才看到
我得和你谈谈

38
00:04:35,001 --> 00:04:37,128
I don't want to go over it any more.
我不想再说了

39
00:04:37,462 --> 00:04:39,881
Things haven't been right
for a long time,
我知道很多事是日积月累的

40
00:04:40,131 --> 00:04:42,926
but it'll be different,
like in the beginning.
但一定会有所改变
就像开始时那样

41
00:04:43,217 --> 00:04:44,969
Just be patient
and I'll work things out.
请有点耐性，我会想办法

42
00:04:45,219 --> 00:04:48,181
I have been patient
and I've tried to help,
我一直都很有耐性
并尝试去帮助你

43
00:04:48,473 --> 00:04:51,100
but you wouldn't even let me do that.
但你甚至不让我这样做

44
00:04:52,685 --> 00:04:55,188
Don't you feel anything for me
any more?
你对我已没有感觉？

45
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:59,400
It takes so many things
to make love last.
令爱情长久，要有很多因素

46
00:04:59,609 --> 00:05:01,694
Most of all, it takes respect.
最重要是彼此尊重

47
00:05:01,986 --> 00:05:04,989
I can't live with a man
I don't respect!
我不能与我不尊重的人生活

48
00:05:11,246 --> 00:05:12,789
What a pisser.
真惹人讨厌

49
00:05:13,039 --> 00:05:14,832
(小说)

50
